uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network

Class NMatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network.NMatcher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMatcher
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NDirectMatcher, ORMatcher

    public abstract class NMatcher
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMatcher
    Abstract base-class for implementations of IMatcher that operate on the intermediate network-based representation.

    The instance-level frames that are passed to the implemented methods, are converted into instantiations of the network-based representation, and then passed to the corresponding abstract methods.

    The matching process can be customised by adding one or more pre-processors to modify the networks that will be passed to the abstract methods (see addPreProcessor(uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.network.NProcessor)).
